As we get older, our eyes go through some changes. These five tips for healthy
eyes will help you stay on top of your eye health and prevent vision loss.
### Keeping your eyes open on optical health
One in three people living with diabetes will develop some form of diabetic
vision loss over their lifetime. It’s important to look after your eyes, and
there are a number of things you can do to reduce your risks.
